{"abstract":[{"text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"URL.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNRasterTileSource(im)initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","symbolKind":"method","title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"instancetype"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"configurationURL:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSURL"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"configurationURL"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A string that uniquely identifies the source in the style to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which it is added.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"identifier"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A URL to a TileJSON configuration file describing the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source’s contents and other metadata."}]}],"name":"configurationURL"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An initialized raster tile source."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After initializing and configuring the source, add it to a map view’s style","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"using the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:","isActive":true},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL may be a full HTTP or HTTPS URL or canonical URL. The URL should","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point to a JSON file that conforms to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TileJSON specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If a Mapbox URL is specified, this source uses a tile size of 256. For all","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other tilesets, the default value is 512. (See the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","type":"reference"},{"text":" documentation for more information about tile","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sizes.) If you need to use a tile size other than the default, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:tileSize:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterTileSource/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterTileSource":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNRasterTileSource"}],"title":"MLNRasterTileSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" is a map content source that supplies raster image tiles","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to be shown on the map. The location of and metadata about the tiles are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"defined either by an option dictionary or by an external file that conforms to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TileJSON specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A raster tile source is added to an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object along with one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" objects. Use a raster style layer to control the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"appearance of content supplied by the raster tile source.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntilesourceoptiontilesize","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSNumber"},{"type":"text","text":" object containing a floating-point number that specifies the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"width and height (measured in points) at which the map displays each raster"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image tile when the map’s zoom level is an integer. The raster tile source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"scales its images up or down when the map’s zoom level falls between two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"integers."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle":{"ro